\\n**路径**：`packages/design-system/lib/src/molecules/swipe_card.dart`\\n\\n###
用途\\n可拖动/可点击的推荐用户卡片，包含头像、姓名、年龄、距离、Bio。\\n\\n### 
构造函数\\n\\n```dart\\nclass SwipeCard extends StatelessWidget {\\n  const Swip
eCard({\\n    super.key,\\n    required this.avatarUrl,\\n    required this.nick
name,\\n    required this.age,\\n    required this.distance,\\n    this.bio,\\n 
  this.isTopCard = false,\\n    this.dragOffset = Offset.zero,\\n    this.onDrag
Update,\\n    this.onDragEnd,\\n  });\\n\\n  /// 用户头像 URL\\n  final String a
